                     <interp inst="t18291029-182-person1446" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a street-keeper. I received this quart pot from the witness - I went and took the prisoner in bed that night, and found these other articles.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I did the deed, and am very sorry for it -I cannot answer for myself; I leave it to you to do what you think proper with me.</p>
